thread.title: Daniel Kunz
thread.title_full: Aran Sweater Market reviewed by Daniel Kunz

author: Daniel Kunz
title: Daniel Kunz
text: The comfort of wearing ARAN clothing is unprecedented! Wear these sweaters in all weather conditions, don't get wet and stay warm and cozy. The stitching however is often poor and I really hope that ARAN is going to improve the quality of stitching to push the quality limits further.
